# ########## API Documentation ##########

### Tasks #####
#### Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/Tasks
Accept: application/json

### 

#### Create a new task
POST http://localhost:3000/api/Tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Task Title",             // Title of the task (required)
    "date": "2024-10-27",               // Task date (YYYY-MM-DD format)
    "due_date": "2024-10-29",           // Due date of the task (YYYY-MM-DD format)
    "location": "Task Location",        // Location of the task (required)
    "subtasks": ["Subtask 1", "Subtask 2"], // List of subtasks (optional)
    "category": "Task Category",        // Corrected: Category of the task (required)
    "completed": false                   // Completion status (default: false)
}

