### HolidayTasks ##### 

#### Get all holiday tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/HolidayTasks
Accept: application/json

### 

#### Create a new holiday task
POST http://localhost:3000/api/HolidayTasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Plan Thanksgiving Dinner", // Title of the holiday task (required)
    "date": "2024-10-27",                 // Task date (YYYY-MM-DD format)
    "location": "Home",                   // Location of the holiday task (optional)
    "subtasks": ["Send invitations", "Buy ingredients", "Set the table"], // List of subtasks (optional)
    "gifts": [],                          // List of gifts (optional)
    "task_for_who": ["Family", "Friends"], // People the task is for (optional)
    "category": "Thanksgiving",           // Corrected: Category of the holiday task (required)
    "completed": false                     // Completion status (default: false)
}
